\\u670d\\u52a1\\u884c\\u4e1a\\u5168\\u666f\\u6df1\\u5ea6\\u5206\\u6790\\u62a5\\u544a\\uff08Iim ...\", \"content\": \"\\u62a5\\u544a\\u6458\\u8981 \\u4e91\\u8ba1\\u7b97\\u670d\\u52a1\\u884c\\u4e1a\\u57282025\\u5e74\\u5448\\u73b0\\u52a0\\u901f\\u6269\\u5f20\\u6001\\u52bf\\uff0c\\u5168\\u7403\\u5e02\\u573a\\u89c4\\u6a21\\u8f832024\\u5e74\\u589e\\u957f18.7%\\uff0c\\u4e2d\\u56fd\\u5e02\\u573a\\u7684\\u589e\\u901f\\u8fbe\\u523024.3%\\uff0c\\u663e\\u8457\\u9ad8\\u4e8e\\u5168\\u7403\\u5e73\\u5747\\u6c34\\u5e73\\u3002 \\u591a\\u6a21\\u6001AI\\u3001\\u8fb9\\u7f18\\u8ba1\\u7b97\\u4e0e\\u91cf\\u5b50\\u8ba1\\u7b97\\u6280\\u672f\\u7684\\u878d\\u5408\\u6210\\u4e3a\\u9a71\\u52a8\\u884c\\u4e1a\\u53d8\\u9769\\u7684\\u6838\\u5fc3\\u8981\\u7d20\\uff0c\\u5934\\u90e8\\u4f01\\u4e1a\\u7684\\u57fa\\u7840\\u8bbe\\u65bd\\u6295\\u8d44\\u540c\\u6bd4\\u589e\\u52a032%\\uff0c\\u533a\\u57df\\u5316\\u90e8\\u7f72\\u7b56\\u7565\\u8fdb...\", \"img_src\": \"\", \"iframe_src\": \"\", \"audio_src\": \"\", \"thumbnail\": \"\", \"publishedDate\": null, \"pubdate\": \"\", \"length\": null, \"views\": \"\", \"author\": \"\", \"metadata\": \"\", \"priority\": \"\", \"engines\": [\"duckduckgo\"], \"open_group\": false, \"close_group\": false, \"positions\": [9], \"score\": 0.1111111111111111, \"category\": \"general\", \"url\": \"https://www.iim.net.cn/91/view-70771-1.html\", \"engine\": \"duckduckgo\", \"parsed_url\": [\"https\", \"www.iim.net.cn\", \"/91/view-70771-1.html\", \"\", \"\", \"\"]}, {\"template\": \"default.html\", \"title\": \"Aws\\u3001Gcp\\uff08\\u8c37\\u6b4c\\u4e91\\uff09\\u3001\\u963f\\u91cc\\u4e91\\u6700\\u65b0\\u52a8\\u6001\\uff1a\\u4e91\\u8ba1\\u7b97\\u884c\\u4e1a\\u8d8b\\u52bf ...\", \"content\": \"\\u968f\\u7740\\u5168\\u7403\\u6570\\u5b57\\u5316\\u8f6c\\u578b\\u4e0e\\u4eba\\u5de5\\u667a\\u80fd\\u7684\\u6d6a\\u6f6e\\uff0c\\u4e91\\u8ba1\\u7b97\\u884c\\u4e1a\\u6b63\\u5feb\\u901f\\u8fdb\\u5165\\u65b0\\u9636\\u6bb5\\u3002 \\u4f01\\u4e1a\\u5bf9 \\u7b97\\u529b\\u3001AI\\u8bad\\u7ec3\\u3001\\u6570\\u636e\\u5b89\\u5168\\u3001\\u5168\\u7403\\u5408\\u89c4 \\u7684\\u9700\\u6c42\\u4e0d\\u65ad\\u63d0\\u5347\\uff0c\\u4e91\\u670d\\u52a1\\u5546\\u4eec\\u4e5f\\u5728\\u52a0\\u901f\\u66f4\\u65b0\\u8fed\\u4ee3\\u3002 \\u4f5c\\u4e3a\\u884c\\u4e1a\\u4e09\\u5927\\u6838\\u5fc3\\u73a9\\u5bb6\\uff0c AWS\\u3001GCP\\uff08\\u8c37\\u6b4c\\u4e91\\uff09\\u3001\\u963f\\u91cc\\u4e91 \\u6b63\\u5728\\u5168\\u7403\\u8303\\u56f4\\u5185\\u5c55\\u5f00\\u6fc0\\u70c8\\u7ade\\u4e89\\u3002\", \"img_src\": \"\", \"iframe_src\": \"\", \"audio_src\": \"\", \"thumbnail\": \"\", \"publishedDate\": null, \"pubdate\": \"\", \"length\": null, \"views\": \"\", \"author\": \"\", \"metadata\": \"\", \"priority\": \"\", \"engines\": [\"duckduckgo\"], \"open_group\": false, \"close_group\": false, \"positions\": [10], \"score\": 0.1, \"category\": \"general\", \"url\": \"https://www.91-cloud.com/blog/2025/09/29/aws-gcp-%E8%B0%B7%E6%AD%8C%E4%BA%91-%E9%98%BF%E9%87%8C%E4%BA%91-%E6%9C%80%E6%96%B0%E5%8A%A8%E6%80%81/\", \"engine\": \"duckduckgo\", \"parsed_url\": [\"https\", \"www.91-cloud.com\", \"/blog/2025/09/29/aws-gcp-%E8%B0%B7%E6%AD%8C%E4%BA%91-%E9%98%BF%E9%87%8C%E4%BA%91-%E6%9C%80%E6%96%B0%E5%8A%A8%E6%80%81/\", \"\", \"\", \"\"]}], \"answers\": [], \"corrections\": [], \"infoboxes\": [], \"suggestions\": [], \"unresponsive_engines\": [[\"brave\", \"Suspended: too many requests\"], [\"startpage\", \"parsing error\"]]}","finalAnswer":null,"durationMs":1027}

event:agent_step
data:{"iteration":1,"action":"FINISH","plan":null,"thought":"搜索到了丰富的云计算行业动态信息，涵盖了市场规模、AI驱动、政策环境、主要厂商动态等多个维度。我可以综合这些信息给用户一个全面的回答。","toolName":null,"toolInput":null,"observation":null,"finalAnswer":"最近云计算行业有几个非常值得关注的动态，我帮你梳理一下：\n\n### 一、市场规模持续高速增长\n- 2024年我国云计算市场规模达 **8288亿元**，同比增长 **34.4%**，增速显著高于全球平均水平（全球约18.7%）。\n- 预计到 **2030年**，我国云计算市场规模将突破 **3万亿元**。\n\n### 二、AI驱动\"云智一体\"成为主旋律\n- 云计算正从单纯的资源供给转向价值创造，**AI大模型**推动智能算力需求激增，AIIaaS、AIPaaS、MaaS等全新服务体系加速形成。\n- 主要云厂商纷纷聚焦 **AI原生与算力升级**，全栈AI云服务成为竞争焦点。\n\n### 三、政策与标准化建设加速\n- 国家层面出台了 **《云计算综合标准化体系建设指南（2025版）》**，为云计算与人工智能的深度融合奠定制度基础。\n- 中国信通院发布了 **《云计算蓝皮书（2025年）》**，聚焦人工智能时代下全球云计算发展重点。\n\n### 四、头部厂商加速布局\n- **AWS、谷歌云、阿里云**等全球三大核心玩家在全球范围内展开激烈竞争，基础设施投资同比增长32%。\n- 国内方面，**腾讯云、华为云、阿里云**等巨头加速向\"云智一体\"演进，百度云等头部厂商领跑市场。\n\n### 五、技术融合拓展边界\n- 多模态AI、**边缘计算**、**量子计算**与云计算的融合创新，正在进一步拓展云计算的边界，形成智能化、场景化、全栈化的技术底座。\n\n总的来说，2025年的云计算行业正处于 **AI驱动的深度变革期**，从基础设施到服务模式都在快速迭代。","durationMs":0}

